00:28:47,460 --> 00:28:49,020
I call them the cloud team.

704
00:28:49,020 --> 00:28:50,610
They're usually infrastructure.

705
00:28:50,610 --> 00:28:52,230
In my case, they're a
former infrastructure team,

706
00:28:52,230 --> 00:28:54,030
I rebranded cloud services.

707
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:55,653
This could be DevOps folks,

708
00:28:56,820 --> 00:29:00,750
but these are the people who
are gonna do it, hands on.

