00:47:44,190 --> 00:47:45,023
and then go fast.

1189
00:47:45,023 --> 00:47:46,290
You get your migration done quickly.

1190
00:47:46,290 --> 00:47:48,510
It should be non-event,
get to the fun stuff.

1191
00:47:48,510 --> 00:47:51,746
Simplicity is how you're
gonna do it primarily.

1192
00:47:51,746 --> 00:47:55,380
Simplicity increases
speed and de-risks things

